text: CHRISTIANSTED, U.S. Virgin Islands, Sept.  20, 2019  (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- Front Yard Residential Corporation (“Front Yard” or the “Company”) (NYSE: RESI) announced today that its Board of Directors has declared a quarterly cash dividend of $0.15 per share of common stock. Front Yard will pay this quarterly dividend on October 11, 2019 to all stockholders of record as of the close of business on September 30, 2019.
title: Front Yard Residential Corporation Announces Quarterly Cash Dividend
